        public Ms2Query(String mgfQuery,
                int index,
                boolean disableCommentSupport,
                boolean ignoreWrongPeaks)
         throws PgatkIOException
        Generates a Ms2Query from a mgf part representing an Ms2Query (including "BEGIN IONS" and "END IONS")
        Parameters:
        mgfQuery - the mgf part to parse
        index - RAW Original scan Number
        disableCommentSupport - true to disable comment support, false otherwise
        Throws:
        PgatkIOException - any problems parsing the mgf part
